{"tid":1144432,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 一人一個尷尬經歷","createTime":"2019-05-08T05:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T17:54:32.000Z","uid":60207,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e651af60ae640b70f33ffd786705633498c3fd3d","tid":1144432,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:38:50.000Z","msg":"記得有年大學有年去參加啲咩語文興趣班，身邊啲朋友都冇興趣得我自己報咗，入到去求其揀左最高嗰排位坐低咗，咁坐低嗰陣隔離嗰位都坐咗個男仔，傾傾下計知道咗佢係香港人就喺度吹水啦，途中啲人都一路入緊課室，咁我望緊啲人入黎既時候發覺有個女仔幾靚女，之後我就同個男仔開心Share啦，話:喂，望下十一點方向，有靚女喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲好似幾大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，俾你你屌唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？之後佢本身喺度周圍望睇下我講緊邊個，嗰樣都好興奮咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到佢望清楚 佢個樣係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我見到佢咁我仲諗緊咩事呢，之後佢揮手叫果個女仔過嚟，同我講話呢個係佢阿妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗屌奶嘢，後尾成程我冇再提過任何女仔，喺度係咁講其他話題分散注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成堂個感覺好柒好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過後尾同個男仔做左幾Fd既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a25451007cf7068eb6c4581f793d8baf0e6fc9c","tid":1144432,"uid":26081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"阿妹呢"},{"pid":"3974ded3cf436887fd49cf9503457aa8b27be80b","tid":1144432,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0176e51ed5b544cbc89fdc05865abfd4492e1287","tid":1144432,